name: AMEPreset

methods.name: requestAudioChannelConfiguration
methods.description: Request the audio channel configuration of this preset from AME. An event with type AMEAudioChannelConfigurationEvent.EVENT_RequestAudioChannelConfigurationSuccess or AMEAudioChannelConfigurationEvent.EVENT_RequestAudioChannelConfigurationError will be sent to notify about success or failure.
methods.longdesc: Request the audio channel configuration of this preset from AME.
